CategoryActivity - Class in it.polimi.dima.mediatracker.activities
Activity that contains: - on tablets: both the "content" of a category page (media items list, suggestions) and the details (form) in a double-pane layout - on phones: only the "content" of a category page For this reason on tablets the activity manages both a ContentAbstractFragment and a FormMediaItemAbstractFragment, while on phones it manages only the former (the latter is managed by OnlyMediaItemFormActivity)
